* Iron Raptor only slightly noticed the sadness in the crew which Mantle 
ruled, trying to keep Prowl's head from slipping to the ground.
But she was suddenly rewarded from the strain when Prowl transformed back 
into robot mode, falling onto her knees nearly in surprise and slipping her 
arms around his chest.
The first thing she did was stroke a hand over his head to see if the damage 
Element had caused to his SBM had been passed on to his robot mode. Sighing 
in relief that none of the damage was transfurred she looked down at him, 
shaking him slightly to try and awaken him.
She looked up at Cinder as she seemed run forward, kneeling at Prowl's side. 
She saw that she was probably trying to pick him up.*

" It's ok, I got him."

* Iron Raptor looked back at Mantle as he came forward more, gripping Prowl 
more tightly as she moved to ger to her feet, trying to take him with her.*

" Yes, as a matter of fact. You can all halp by keeping close to the CF, 
there'll be a meeting shortly."
